  "detailed_description": "<h1>Our New Enchant Games</h1><p></p><br><h1>Our New Enchant Games</h1><p></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1983420/extras/4ba2ce9d716eb922be294d5e56d7ff37.poster.avif?t=1680126572\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1983420/extras/4ba2ce9d716eb922be294d5e56d7ff37.webm?t=1680126572\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1983420/extras/4ba2ce9d716eb922be294d5e56d7ff37.mp4?t=1680126572\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>Just play and chill</strong><br><br>LoFi Hotel is a comforting game about collecting cute guests and songs while enjoying Lofi music. Your hotel is a flying turtle, blessed with an oak tree on its shell waiting for you to explore a world of flying islands to rescue lost little animals.<br><br>Music is the key! Collect dozens of different songs. They sound different depending on which musicians are in your party.  <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1983420/extras/38793fbbf0e764a1ef9afb3cf3e0f973.poster.avif?t=1680126572\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1983420/extras/38793fbbf0e764a1ef9afb3cf3e0f973.webm?t=1680126572\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1983420/extras/38793fbbf0e764a1ef9afb3cf3e0f973.mp4?t=1680126572\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>Highlights</strong><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>  Enjoy more than 60 minutes of original sound track composed exclusively for the game.<br></li><li>  Go through dozens of levels in beautiful 2D scenarios.<br></li><li>  Admire the charming hand-crafted animations.<br></li><li>  Gain gems to unlock rooms to get more and more guests<br></li><li>  Collect dozens of different cute guests.<br></li><li>  Enjoy hours of comforting and relaxing gameplay. <br></li><li>  Explore a world map to find new songs and guests in the sky islands</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1983420/extras/f4bf1339395e50aae1d8c60060222eb4.poster.avif?t=1680126572\" width=600 height=110 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1983420/extras/f4bf1339395e50aae1d8c60060222eb4.webm?t=1680126572\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1983420/extras/f4bf1339395e50aae1d8c60060222eb4.mp4?t=1680126572\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1983420/extras/NEW_GAME.gif?t=1680126572\" /></span>",
  "about_the_game": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1983420/extras/4ba2ce9d716eb922be294d5e56d7ff37.poster.avif?t=1680126572\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1983420/extras/4ba2ce9d716eb922be294d5e56d7ff37.webm?t=1680126572\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1983420/extras/4ba2ce9d716eb922be294d5e56d7ff37.mp4?t=1680126572\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>Just play and chill</strong><br><br>LoFi Hotel is a comforting game about collecting cute guests and songs while enjoying Lofi music. Your hotel is a flying turtle, blessed with an oak tree on its shell waiting for you to explore a world of flying islands to rescue lost little animals.<br><br>Music is the key! Collect dozens of different songs. They sound different depending on which musicians are in your party.  <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1983420/extras/38793fbbf0e764a1ef9afb3cf3e0f973.poster.avif?t=1680126572\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1983420/extras/38793fbbf0e764a1ef9afb3cf3e0f973.webm?t=1680126572\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1983420/extras/38793fbbf0e764a1ef9afb3cf3e0f973.mp4?t=1680126572\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>Highlights</strong><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>  Enjoy more than 60 minutes of original sound track composed exclusively for the game.<br></li><li>  Go through dozens of levels in beautiful 2D scenarios.<br></li><li>  Admire the charming hand-crafted animations.<br></li><li>  Gain gems to unlock rooms to get more and more guests<br></li><li>  Collect dozens of different cute guests.<br></li><li>  Enjoy hours of comforting and relaxing gameplay. <br></li><li>  Explore a world map to find new songs and guests in the sky islands</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1983420/extras/f4bf1339395e50aae1d8c60060222eb4.poster.avif?t=1680126572\" width=600 height=110 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1983420/extras/f4bf1339395e50aae1d8c60060222eb4.webm?t=1680126572\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1983420/extras/f4bf1339395e50aae1d8c60060222eb4.mp4?t=1680126572\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1983420/extras/NEW_GAME.gif?t=1680126572\" /></span>",
